$ Bitcoin core: testing

After compiling the sources, there are two executables under → development/Crypto-Currencies/Bitcoin/clients/Bitcoin-Core/dev: `test_bitcoin` and `test_bitcoin_fuzzy`.

In order to reduce the time to execute the testcases, the number of test cases can be limited, for example with
code {
./test_bitcoin --run_tests=addrman_tests
code }

{ Boost test framework

  The tests use the → development/languages/C-C-plus-plus/boost/test[boost test framework]

}
